desc: We manufacture and sell products for dental, medical industry, and general PPE user. Our range includes custom EVA blanks and foils for mouthguards, gum shields, face visors, bleaching trays, splints, impression trays, dental packaging and boxes. We offer wider range of colours and custom branding options.

layout.text: Choose from wide range of standard or design your own mouthguards from a selection of 36 colours and numerous patterns
